name: I'm No Saint ring by Cristina Scabbia
description:
"It's the inner kid inside of us that wants to kick out and get whatever he wants. A free spirit, a fierce presence, laughs at curveballs life throws at him and he rises above everything and all. He knows he is perfect with his imperfections." 

Designed by Cristina Scabbia, lead singer of Italian rockers Lacuna Coil. 
35grams of solid sterling silver. This very special ring comes in the SCA laser etched chrome case and a printed card featuring the concept for the design in Cristinas own words. 

Available in sizes L to Z+1

Please state size required when ordering at the Paypal checkout.

name: Black leather cowboy hat with silver crow skull
description:
The ulitmate rock n roll accessory! 
This is a genuine black leather cowboy hat with shapeable wired brim. The crow skull mounted on the front is cast from an actual crow skull in solid sterling silver and securely riveted to the hat. 

Available in the following sizes:

57cm (small)
58cm (medium)
59cm (large)
60cm (extra large)

Please state size required during the Paypal checkout.

name: Necroriser Necroring
description:
Heavyweight (approx. 45grams), solid sterling silver skull ring with the Necroriser logo deep engraved on the forehead.
  
Available in sizes L to Z+4 Please state ring size when ordering.

name: Small Skull Pendant
description:
A subtle but rock n roll skull pendant! The skull is 10mm high and made from solid sterling silver. Hung on a fine, delicate sterling silver belcher chain. 

Please state chain length you require when ordering at the checkout.

name: Bird Skull ring
description:
Beautiful bird skull ring created from a real found bird skull. Features split shoulders flowing into the base of the skull and beak. Made in solid sterling silver.

Available in sizes K-Z. 

Please state size when ordering.

name: Runic band
description:
Runic bands handmade to order in solid sterling silver. 
These rings are fully customizable so each one is totally unique. Up to 12 letters can be set on to the outside of the ring. Let us know what letters you require and we will convert them to Elder Futhark runic letters. Can be a great alternative to engagement rings.
(price is per piece)

Available in sizes K to Z+2.
(please ensure you let us know your correct finger size when ordering as these rings cannot be adjusted once made).

name: Twins Of Evil torc bangle (Mens size)
description: Hand made solid sterling silver torc bangle with matching evil skull heads.

name: Twins Of Evil torc bangle (Ladies size)
description: Hand made solid sterling silver torc bangle with matching evil skull heads.

name: Morbid Angel Ring
description:
The Official Morbid Angel ring as worn by the band themselves. 
Approx 50g of solid sterling silver! Featuring the bands' iconic  Blasphegram logo on the top with two goatheads carved either side on the shoulders. Comes in a high gloss, ebony presentation box with a black leather cushioned interior and sterling silver blasphegram on the lid. 
The rings are individually numbered and limited to only 33 pieces.
Available in sizes P to Z+4 Please state ring size when ordering.
(You can download a printable ring size guide from our main site www.seventhcircleartworks.com)

name: Ace Of Spades Ring

name: The Mi Ruina Ring
description:
Designed by Tairrie B, lead vocalist of the Los Angeles based metal band My Ruin.  Created in honor of My Ruins' new 7th album "A Southern Revelation" this spectacular sterling silver, 3-part jointed armour ring incorporates 4 plain bands and 2 rosary bands on each side with the Spanish inscription Mi Ruina Por Vida (My Ruin For Life) engraved into the knuckle band. Each ring is hand crafted, oxidized and smoked to give it a subtle vintage, aged effect.  
The Mi Ruina Ring is also featured on Tairrie B in the bands video for the song "Tennessee Elegy" which she co directed and comes scented in her custom blended signature oil inside a black velvet pouch with a personalized signed card.  

Available in sizes L- Z+2 for men and women. 

Please state size required when ordering.

name: The Mi Ruina Ring II
description:
The second ring in the Mi Ruina trilogy set of wearable art designed by Tairrie B of My Ruin.

This more simplified ring design is made of a full court shape band with the separate center piece featuring the Spanish inscription 'i uina Por Vida' which means 'My Ruin For Life' riveted to it from the outside, giving a hinged movement to the outer band. Each ring is hand crafted in London, oxidized and smoked to give it a subtle vintage, aged effect and A true statement piece if ever there was one.
 
Available in sizes L - Z+2 

Please state size required when ordering.

name: The Mi Ruina Ring III
description:
The third ring in the Mi Ruina trilogy set of wearable art designed by Tairrie B of My Ruin.

This beauty of this simple heavy weight sterling silver band is that it is hand crafted in London, oxidized and smoked to give it a subtle vintage, aged effect and features the Spanish inscription 'i uina Por Vida' which means 'My Ruin For Life'. A true statement piece if ever there was one.
 
Available in sizes L - Z+2 

Please state size required when ordering.
